–Daj no.

00:05:21.478 --> 00:05:23.939
To je Albert Brown,
sijajni producent.

00:05:24.148 --> 00:05:25.899
Kako si?
–Vojska nam ga je poslala.

00:05:25.940 --> 00:05:27.860
