bom jaz v maturantski obleki.

00:09:24.971 --> 00:09:26.599
Mamljivo.

00:09:30.019 --> 00:09:32.020
Hej, mali. Kaj dogaja?

00:09:32.480 --> 00:09:34.899
Rasteš,
da boš velik kot očka?

00:09:36.067 --> 00:09:37.360
