00:10:32.498 --> 00:10:34.959
ki vam prvo pride na misel,
ampak poslušajte.

00:10:35.042 --> 00:10:36.251
Poslušajte.
–Prav.

00:10:36.293 --> 00:10:37.461
Hilary Swank.

00:10:37.544 --> 00:10:38.962
Vau.
–Kaj?

00:10:39.046 --> 00:10:41.465
V filmu <i>Boys Don't Cry</i>
je dobila oskarja.

00:10:41.548 --> 00:10:43.299
Igrala je punco,
preoblečeno v fanta.

00:10:43.384 --> 00:10:46.511
Vemo, kdo je.
Zakaj se zanima za nas?

00:10:46.595 --> 00:10:48.221
Ker hoče igrati njega.

00:10:50.474 --> 00:10:52.143
O, mater!

00:10:55.687 --> 00:10:57.648
Vem, da morda
ni idealna izbira,

00:10:57.731 --> 00:10:59.524
ampak če se bo zavzela

00:10:59.607 --> 00:11:02.861
