Zakaj 72?

00:21:38.288 --> 00:21:39.289
Hvala.
–Ja, gospod.

00:21:39.373 --> 00:21:40.624
Bravo.
–Bravo.

00:21:40.708 --> 00:21:41.750
Zelo dobro.

00:21:43.669 --> 00:21:46.130
Josh, sestradan sem.

00:21:46.212 --> 00:21:47.839
Bi lahko dobili kos pice

00:21:47.923 --> 00:21:49.799
