ni strahu, da boš izpadel cepec.

00:22:21.624 --> 00:22:23.500
Drek. Za to pa ne skrbi.

00:22:23.625 --> 00:22:25.502
V moji glavi
boš vedno cepec.

00:22:25.627 --> 00:22:27.462
Fantje, vse bo v redu.

00:22:27.546 --> 00:22:30.132
Samo trenutek.
Kje je major McLaurin?

00:22:30.383 --> 00:22:31.592
Drek.

00:22:31.967 --> 00:22:34.427
Lodis, Sykes, poiščita majorja.
Pripeljita ga na konec.

00:22:34.470 --> 00:22:35.637
Razumem.
–Josh?

00:22:35.721 --> 00:22:38.348
Tablete?
